<p><strong>THE MARLBOROUGH MEDAL</strong></p>

<p><em>A special award for Lifetime Contribution to Sport in Marlborough, known as The Marlborough Medal, was introduced in 2013. This prestigious award is also presented on the night, revealing the amazing dedication and community spirit of one of our local champions, who is more often than not a volunteer.</em></p>
